PM India zai halarci bikin faretin ban kwana na haikali a wani wuri da ake takaddama akai
New DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci wani gagarumin biki a wata mai zuwa na wani haikalin 'yan Hindu a wani wuri da ake takaddama a kansa a arewacin Indiya inda aka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 a hannun 'yan Hindu masu wuyar sha'ani a shekarar 1992, a cewar dogarawan da ke kula da aikin ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Yulin, ranar da masu shirya bikin suka ce abin mamaki ne ga mabiya addinin Hindu, amma kuma hakan na zuwa ne a dai-dai lokacin da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta sake farfado da matsayinta na kasa mai cin gashin kanta na jiha daya tilo da Musulmai suka fi yawa, Jamhuriyyar Dimokradiyyar Congo.
Wannan alamari ba zai yiwu a rasa magoya baya da kuma masu adawa da jam'iyyar Modi ta mabiya addinin Hindu Bharatiya Janata Party, ko kuma BJP ba, wadanda bayyanarsu ta shafe shekaru da dama suna kunshe da alkawarurrukan da suka dauka na tsame mulkin Kashmir da kuma gina haikali ga Hindu allah Ram inda masallacin Mughal-era ya taba tsayawa, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya da ke jihar Uttar Pradesh da 'yan uwa suka yi imanin cewa nan ne wurin haihuwar Ram.
Saboda har yanzu cutar Koronabirus na ci gaba da yaduwa a fadin Indiya, wacce ta bayar da rahoton bullar cutar a matsayin irinta ta uku a duniya, bikin za a yada shi ne kai tsaye a gidajen talabijin na kasar kuma za a takaita yawan mahalarta da kuma 'yan kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiyar 'yan kishin Hindu da ke kawance da jam'iyyar BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "cibiyar jituwa ta zamantakewa, da hadin kan kasa da hadewa da kuma farkawa daga jin yaren Hindutva", ko kuma hanyar rayuwar Hindu, a cewar mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal a wata sanarwa da ya fitar a ranar Asabar.
An sasanta rikicin da aka kwashe tsawon lokaci ana yi a kan wurin a shekarar da ta wuce bayan nasarar da jam'iyyar BJP ta samu a zaben da aka yi a kasar.
