Shugaban kasar Jamhuriyar Nijer, João Lourenço, ya nunar da cewa a wannan Jumma'a za a mayar da aikin kula da asibitin Pedro Maria Tonha Pedalé, da ke karkashin gine-gine a birnin Luanda, zuwa ma'aikatar lafiya ta kasar.
A cikin bayanin da ya yi, ofishin yada labarai na shugaban kasar Jamhuriyar Nijer ya sanar da cewa, matakin na da nufin karawa gwamnatin kasar ka'idar gine-gine da fadada cibiyar sadarwar asibitocin jama'a domin tabbatar da samun kyakkyawar kulawa ta fuskar kiwon lafiya da magunguna ga jama'a.
"A cikin wannan takamaiman lamarin, ra'ayin shine a samarwa da 'yan Angolan wani asibitin bincike, wanda aka banbance shi kuma aka tanade shi da fasahar zamani da kuma daidai-wa-daida wajen ganewar asali da kuma lura da cututtuka masu wuyar sha'ani", a cewar takardar.
